點連技好</blockquote><br />\n睇情況</blockquote><br />\n假如打到巴龍得番3分1 開大後對面殘血 應該追上去定食巴龍</blockquote><br />\n卡特頂到巴龍幾耐,二下俾人打返轉頭都似。"},{"pid":"ce664486fd47693016ccdb1c5078797e23c2b3f7","tid":385194,"uid":14910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:36:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f728e9a89d9455bc5a4434dd3df836480e9ac90","tid":385194,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Check左 樓主銅3</blockquote><br />\n唔好起底ok?"},{"pid":"dfcd3568049c2192892c041bcb28ec1687a67072","tid":385194,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"幾時答<br />\n<br />\n覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"c88e50967c774a008693d3f1ba21f75e2db66d98","tid":385194,"uid":25050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"Funny 令我笑咗<br />\n比個正皮你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a454e098e11b3d71a6b030cf43528d5cdac9b1","tid":385194,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Funny 令我笑咗<br />\n比個正皮你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗人認同"},{"pid":"a6c0a2a3f8eaa775277818b05c8b8f8d7ac2cba9","tid":385194,"uid":127611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"爐石有傳<br />\n計返lol都應該有大師實力<br />\n有咩都可以問我"},{"pid":"1c145aa97c4a7950ad4b3761b3a6156a5690ba83","tid":385194,"uid":142725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:23:09.000Z","msg":"本人韓服大師 台服菁英頭50  main sup<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問樓主對韓服職業選手有咩好方法 次次順風變逆風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有次對wolf試過下路比人打到0/7/1 ad0/8/2 但ad唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  懷疑個ad係bang小號<